      "value": "<p>You have a talent for finding hidden weapons and other illicit items, as well as subduing those who refuse to follow the rules. It takes you half as much time as others to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.gZlg2ZKze0erNLmP#search]{Search an Area} using @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.gZlg2ZKze0erNLmP]{Perception}, and you gain a +2 bonus on Perception checks opposing @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.qVEW9HjXQN0ok879]{Sleight of Hand} checks to hide objects, palm objects, or pick pockets. You only take a â€“2 penalty to your attack roll when you use a weapon that deals lethal damage to deal nonlethal damage instead.</p>"
